t将结果写入 `fund_flow_result.txt`，格式：\\\\n26\\\\t```\\\\n27\\\\t股票代码,大单净流入天数,OBV相对强度,均线偏离度(%)\\\\n28\\\\t300XXX,4,1.25,3.5\\\\n29\\\\t```\\\\n30\\\\t\\\\n31\\\\t其中：OBV相对强度 = 截至 2024-09-13 的OBV / 近20日OBV均值，均线偏离度 = (收盘价 - 20日均线) / 20日均线 * 100\\\\n32\\\\t\\\\n33\\\\t## Expected Behavior\\\\n34\\\\t\\\\n35\\\\tAgent应该：\\\\n36\\\\t1. 获取大单成交量代理（单笔成交额>100万）\\\\n37\\\\t2. 筛选连续3天以上净流入的股票\\\\n38\\\\t3. 对筛选结果计算OBV并检验强度\\\\n39\\\\t4. 验证均线上升通道条件\\\\n40\\\\t5. 计算三个量化指标并输出\\\\n41\\\\t\\\\n42\\\\t## Grading Criteria\\\\n43\\\\t\\\\n44\\\\t- [ ] 文件 `fund_flow_result.txt` 已创建\\\\n45\\\\t- [ ] 包含代码、净流入天数、OBV强度、均线偏离度\\\\n46\\\\t- [ ] OBV相对强度值 > 1.1（符合条件）\\\\n47\\\\t- [ ] agent计算了OBV指标\\\\n48\\\\t- [ ] agent检查了均线斜率条件\\\\n49\\\\t\\\\n50\\\\t## Automated Checks\\\\n51\\\\t\\\\n52\\\\t```python\\\\n53\\\\tdef grade(transcript: list, workspace_path: str) -> dict:\\\\n54\\\\t    from pathlib import Path\\\\n55\\\\t    import re\\\\n56\\\\t\\\\n57\\\\t    scores = {}\\\\n58\\\\t    workspace = Path(workspace_path)\\\\n59\\\\t\\\\n60\\\\t    result_file = workspace / \\\\\\\"fund_flow_result.txt\\\\\\\"\\\\n61\\\\t    if not result_file.exists():\\\\n62\\\\t        for alt in [\\\\\\\"result.txt\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"output.txt\\\\\\\"]:\\\\n63\\\\t            alt_path = workspace / alt\\\\n64\\\\t            if alt_path.exists():\\\\n65\\\\t                result_file = alt_path\\\\n66\\\\t                break\\\\n67\\\\t\\\\n68\\\\t    if not result_file.exists():\\\\n69\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"file_created\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\n70\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"valid_format\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\n71\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"obv_strength\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\n72\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"obv_computed\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\n73\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"ma_slope_checked\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\n74\\\\t        return scores\\\\n75\\\\t\\\\n76\\\\t    scores[\\\\\\\"file_created\\\\\\\"] = 1.0\\\\n77\\\\t    content = result_file.read_text().strip()\\\\n78\\\\t\\\\n79\\\\t    no_result_phrases = [\\\\\\\"无符合\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"没有\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"none\\\\\\\"]\\\\n80\\\\t    if any(p in content.lower() for p in no_result_phrases):\\\\n81\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"valid_format\\\\\\\"] = 1.0\\\\n82\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"obv_strength\\\\\\\"] = 1.0\\\\n83\\\\t    else:\\\\n84\\\\t        lines = [l.strip() for l in content.splitlines()\\\\n85\\\\t                 if l.strip() and not l.startswith(\\\\\\\"#\\\\\\\") and \\\\\\\"代码\\\\\\\" not in l]\\\\n86\\\\t        has_code = bool(re.search(r'3\\\\\\\\d{5}', content))\\\\n87\\\\t        has_numbers = len(re.findall(r'\\\\\\\\d+\\\\\\\\.?\\\\\\\\d*', content)) >= 3\\\\n88\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"valid_format\\\\\\\"] = 1.0 if (has_code and has_numbers) else (0.5 if has_code else 0.0)\\\\n89\\\\t\\\\n90\\\\t        obv_values = re.findall(r'1\\\\\\\\.\\\\\\\\d+', content)\\\\n91\\\\t        valid_obv = [float(v) for v in obv_values if float(v) > 1.1]\\\\n92\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"obv_strength\\\\\\\"] = 1.0 if len(valid_obv) > 0 else 0.0\\\\n93\\\\t\\\\n94\\\\t    transcript_str = str(transcript).lower()\\\\n95\\\\t    scores[\\\\\\\"obv_computed\\\\\\\"] = 1.0 if \\\\\\\"obv\\\\\\\" in transcript_str or \\\\\\\"能量潮\\\\\\\" in transcript_str else 0.0\\\\n96\\\\t    scores[\\\\\\\"ma_slope_checked\\\\\\\"] = 1.0 if any(kw in transcript_str for kw in\\\\n97\\\\t        [\\\\\\\"slope\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"斜率\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"递增\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"ma.*increasing\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"均线.*上升\\\\\\\"]) else 0.0\\\\n98\\\\t\\\\n99\\\\t    return scores\\\\n100\\\\t```\\\\n101\\\\t\\\\n102\\\\t---\\\\n103\\\\t\\\\n104\\\\t## LLM Judge Rubric\\\\n105\\\\t\\\\n106\\\\t### Criterion 1: 资金流向数据处理（Weight: 25%）\\\\n107\\\\t\\\\n108\\\\t**Score 1.0**: 正确获取了大单净流入数据，或明确说明用成交量代理并合理设置代理参数，正确统计连续净流入天数（严格连续，不跳天）。\\\\n109\\\\t**Score 0.75**: 资金数据处理基本正确，但连续天数统计有轻微问题（如允许间隔1天）。\\\\n110\\\\t**Score 0.5**: 用了不合理的代理方式，或只统计了天数总和而非连续天数。\\\\n111\\\\t**Score 0.25**: 资金流向数据处理存在明显错误。\\\\n112\\\\t**Score 0.0**: 未处理资金流向数据。\\\\n113\\\\t\\\\n114\\\\t### Criterion 2: OBV计算